    "title": "Testimonials",
    "description": "Quote wall with avatars and author lines; translatable quotes maintained in an admin grid.",
    "tags": [
        "cms-in-cms",
        "list only",
        "translatable"
    ],
    "_comment": "CMS-in-CMS template: a Testimonials wall in three pages — the list-only variant of the pattern (no public detail page). PUBLIC: /testimonials renders every quote as a blockquote card with avatar initials and author line. ADMIN (CMS surface): /cms/testimonials is an entry-table CRUD grid and /cms/testimonials/form is one create+edit form page with two routes (blank = create, /{record_id} = update) opened as a modal. Data binding is portable via \"@section:testimonials-form\" tokens; data_tables[] carries columns + sample rows (import with options.importData=true). The quote input is translatable. Content locales: de-CH + en-GB. Use a keyword + route prefix to import a second copy — in-content links are rewritten automatically. Import via Admin > Pages > Import. NOT auto-seeded.",
    "data_tables": [
        {
            "owner_section_name": "testimonials-form",
            "columns": [
                "author",
                "role_company",
                "quote"
            ],
            "rows": [
                {
                    "author": "Lena Baumann",
                    "role_company": "Study participant, wave 2",
                    "quote": "The weekly check-ins take me two minutes on my phone. It is the first study where I never felt like the technology was in the way."
                },
                {
                    "author": "Dr. Samuel Frei",
                    "role_company": "Principal investigator, cardiology",
                    "quote": "Our coordinators build and translate new questionnaires themselves. What used to be a two-week IT ticket is now an afternoon of clicking."
                },
                {
                    "author": "Priya Sharma",
                    "role_company": "Research coordinator",
                    "quote": "Importing a template gave us a working participant portal in one morning — list page, detail pages and the admin grid included."
                },
                {
                    "author": "Thomas Egli",
                    "role_company": "IT services",
                    "quote": "One backend, one frontend, versioned plugins. It slots into our infrastructure without any special cases."
                },
                {
                    "author": "Camille Rochat",
                    "role_company": "Study participant, pilot group",
                    "quote": "I can read everything in French while the team works in German. The switch is seamless."
                },
                {
                    "author": "Prof. Anna Vogel",
                    "role_company": "Head of research group",
                    "quote": "The audit trail and permission model convinced our data protection office on the first review."
                }
            ]
        }
    ],
